      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>roughly</p><p>Heat a pot with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]<strong> </span>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until beginning to break down</p><p>Whilst the tomatoes are cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
