    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is in the oven, wash your <strong>lettuce</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove 2 <strong>outer leaves</strong> per person from the<strong> lettuce</strong> and chop the <strong>inner core[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> into rounds</p>",
