    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>gluten free</strong> <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half</p><p>Add the<strong> brioche halves</strong> to the other side of the tray</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 2-3 min or until the cheese flavour slices have melted and the brioche is warmed through</p>",
