    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Assemble your burgers by topping the <strong>warmed brioche base</strong> with a dollop of <strong>tomato relish</strong>, 2 <strong>lettuce leaves</strong>, a <strong>cheezy meat-free patty</strong>,<strong> </strong>some<strong> shallot rounds</strong> and the<strong> warmed brioche lid </strong>– this is your <strong>ultimate veggie cheezeburger</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> ultimate veggie cheezeburger</strong> with the <strong>rosemary chips</strong>,<strong> lettuce quarters</strong> and any <strong>remaining tomato relish</strong> to the side for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
